{
  "stem": "19895.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 76.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because you go out only between 11:00 and 5:00 So herd of people were leaving the buildings, going to the stores.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then in the stores, they were pushed away, because other people wanted to buy, the rest of the Budapest population.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And people were-- extortion of prices, they were-- they were asking higher prices for food from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because they knew that they-- they have to go back to their buildings in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And sometime, there were some storekeepers who were decent and helped and-- and gave food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And sometime, Father came home empty handed that he couldn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I recall one occasion when he stepped out of the building trying to get to the store much sooner, five minutes-- left before five minutes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And from a neighboring barber shop, a military-uniformed person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's something which the Hungarian Jews feared most.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was not the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was the so-called [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Chander. ?] They were the-- They wee a different organization from the city police-- the country police, the [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Chander. ?] And they had some very attractive uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I admired the uniform, but did I fear them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that person grabbed my father and beat him up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He says you left your building before time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And father came back with bleeding nose and then-- and bruises from being beaten up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Just that he left five minutes too soon the building, and this guy from the barber shop have seen that father sneaked out sooner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that's just one incident how it happened, and what went on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then-- then came the days that one morning in that Jewish house, Jewish apartment building, at-- all over in the city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we are getting to the months of October, when one day they came up-- came into the building.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
